substep.action:
gh pr comment {{pr_number}} --body "## Review Feedback Summary

@gemini-code-assist All feedback has been addressed.

{{summary_table}}

Please re-review the changes."

Update {{bundle_dir}}/pr-cycle-state.md frontmatter:
- iteration_count: {{iteration_count + 1}}
- last_action_time: current ISO 8601
- last_action: RE_REVIEW_REQUESTED
- pr_number: {{pr_number}}
- pr_url: {{pr_url}}
- threads_addressed_total: cumulative
- threads_declined_total: cumulative
- threads_deferred_total: cumulative

Body includes per-iteration log:
## Iteration {{iteration_count}}
- Threads: {{n_address}} addressed, {{n_decline}} declined, {{n_defer}} deferred
- Commit: {{fix_commit_sha}} (if any)
- Re-review requested at: {{timestamp}}
